{{#freestyle-subsection name='product-tile' section=section}}

  {{#freestyle-usage 'product-tile' title='Product Tile'}}
    {{c-product-tile
    title=products.items.[0].title
    image=products.items.[0].image
    description=products.items.[0].description
    rating=products.items.[0].rating
    price=products.items.[0].price
    unit=products.items.[0].unit
    currency=products.items.[0].currency
    isDiscounted=false
    }}
  {{/freestyle-usage}}

  {{#freestyle-note 'product-tile:notes'}}
  A product tile displays a listing for a product with a title, image, description, ration and price in a give unit.

  It depends on the c-button component to display the "buy" button.
  {{/freestyle-note}}

